you tell them it ain't me.

268
00:26:12,018 --> 00:26:14,952
<i>Tell us what you know.</i>

269
00:26:16,021 --> 00:26:19,155
Yeah, I passed through here
last night.

270
00:26:19,157 --> 00:26:23,292
