272
00:26:29,900 --> 00:26:32,934
String him up!

273
00:26:32,936 --> 00:26:37,238
That ain't the way it happened.
I swear.

274
00:26:37,240 --> 00:26:41,742
We found the map...
To murrell's treasure.

275
00:26:41,744 --> 00:26:46,346
And then Joe and doc got to fightin'.
Murrell's treasure.

276
00:26:46,348 --> 00:26:49,916
You hear that, people? More
drunk talk from muff Potter.

277
00:26:49,918 --> 00:26:54,053
Murrell's lost treasure
is an old wives' tale.

278
00:26:54,055 --> 00:26:56,889
I know the history
of this entire county,

279
00:26:56,891 --> 00:26:59,291
and I'm telling you
it doesn't exist.

280
00:26:59,293 --> 00:27:02,861
But I seen the map!

281
00:27:02,863 --> 00:27:05,897
I say you're lyin'.

282
00:27:05,899 --> 00:27:09,133
I say there ain't no map.

283
00:27:09,135 --> 00:27:12,903
- And there never was.
<i>- String him up!</i>

284
00:27:14,773 --> 00:27:17,673
Who all thinks muff Potter's
a drunk,

285
00:27:17,675 --> 00:27:21,943
