raise your hand!

286
00:27:23,980 --> 00:27:27,113
<i>I say we hang him!</i>

287
00:27:30,751 --> 00:27:35,253
<i>All right, folks. Let's just hold on here.
Now, hold on.</i>

288
00:27:35,255 --> 00:27:37,355
Thank you.

289
00:27:39,158 --> 00:27:43,260
Now, you folks wouldn't be trying
to deny me the pleasure...

290
00:27:43,262 --> 00:27:46,962
Of presidin' over a trial,
now would ya?

291
00:27:48,131 --> 00:27:51,365
You all right,
Mr. Potter?

292
00:27:51,367 --> 00:27:54,801
After all, what would be the point
of having a new judge in town...

293
00:27:54,803 --> 00:27:58,037
If you won't let me judge anything?
<i>We all know he's guilty!</i>

294
00:27:58,039 --> 00:28:02,374
Ow! Hey! We all know you're
an idiot, ed dobbins.

295
00:28:02,376 --> 00:28:05,110
Listen to me,
you pointy-headed ghouls.

296
00:28:05,112 --> 00:28:08,379
Muff Potter may be
the scum of the earth,

297
00:28:08,381 --> 00:28:11,715
but he deserves a fair trial,
and I aim to see he gets one.

298
00:28:11,717 --> 00:28:14,417
