299
00:28:14,419 --> 00:28:16,685
I should be able to start hearin'
evidence day after tomorrow.

300
00:28:16,687 --> 00:28:22,123
Settled. Now, the rest of you<i> good
</i> citizens, you be on your way.

301
00:28:22,125 --> 00:28:24,925
