Come on.

302
00:28:24,927 --> 00:28:28,228
Let's go, muff.

303
00:28:35,837 --> 00:28:39,871
I didn't do it, tom.
I swear, I didn't do it.

304
00:28:41,741 --> 00:28:46,977
