We gotta help him.

307
00:28:57,754 --> 00:29:00,454
We ain't gotta do nothin'.

308
00:29:02,024 --> 00:29:04,457
You'd let him hang
for somethin' he didn't do?

309
00:29:04,459 --> 00:29:08,093
It ain't no skin off my back.

310
00:29:08,095 --> 00:29:10,428
What if we could get the map?

311
00:29:10,430 --> 00:29:14,198
We could prove muff was tellin' the truth,
and it wouldn't make us break our oath.

312
00:29:14,200 --> 00:29:18,035
Only one little problem. That
map is in injun Joe's pocket.

313
00:29:18,037 --> 00:29:21,338
Well, if you're scared... why should
I stick my neck out for muff Potter?

314
00:29:21,340 --> 00:29:23,773
'Cause we know he didn't do it.
So?

315
00:29:23,775 --> 00:29:28,010
So not doin' anything about it is wrong.
Says who?

316
00:29:30,047 --> 00:29:32,781
What if it was you in muff's shoes?
It ain't.

317
00:29:32,783 --> 00:29:36,384
What if it was me?
If you was that stupid,

318
00:29:36,386 --> 00:29:39,887
maybe you'd deserve
what was comin' to you.

319
00:29:39,889 --> 00:29:42,155
It's not what friends do, huck.

320
00:29:43,391 --> 00:29:45,824
I thought we was friends.

321
00:29:46,927 --> 00:29:50,028
Maybe I don't know
what you're talkin' about.

322
00:29:55,134 --> 00:29:58,735
