What's the matter, tom?

329
00:30:27,762 --> 00:30:30,529
Oh, nothin'.

330
00:30:33,967 --> 00:30:36,467
You can tell me.

331
00:30:36,469 --> 00:30:40,237
I won't ever tell anybody.

332
00:30:46,211 --> 00:30:48,244
Here.

333
00:30:50,248 --> 00:30:52,881
This is for you.

334
00:30:54,117 --> 00:30:56,216
Thanks.

