336
00:31:01,356 --> 00:31:04,190
No.
How do you do it?

337
00:31:05,393 --> 00:31:09,361
Well, you gotta tell the person
that you love 'im.

338
00:31:10,430 --> 00:31:12,463
Then what?

339
00:31:14,033 --> 00:31:16,333
Well, then you're 'spose
to kiss.

340
00:31:16,335 --> 00:31:19,869
Really?
Sure.

341
00:31:21,939 --> 00:31:26,474
You first. I love you. There.
Now you gotta say it to me.

342
00:31:26,476 --> 00:31:29,877
Turn your face away.

343
00:31:29,879 --> 00:31:34,314
And you can't tell anybody ever.
I won't.

344
00:31:37,385 --> 00:31:40,084
I love you.

345
00:31:42,888 --> 00:31:47,590
Well, I... Guess everything's
done but the kissin' part.

346
00:31:56,232 --> 00:31:58,432
Here.

347
00:31:59,501 --> 00:32:03,603
Oh, tom, it's, it's...
what is it?

348
00:32:03,605 --> 00:32:07,907
It's your engagement ring.
It's beautiful.

349
00:32:07,909 --> 00:32:11,076
It sure is. Why, when I was
engaged to Amy Lawrence, she...

350
00:32:11,078 --> 00:32:14,279
what? You mean,
I'm not the first?

351
00:32:14,281 --> 00:32:17,915
Yeah. But, Becky, that was ages ago.
Two months at least.

352
00:32:17,917 --> 00:32:19,917
I hate you.
What?

353
00:32:19,919 --> 00:32:23,120
I hate you, and I hope you die!

354
00:32:25,491 --> 00:32:28,191
What'd I do?

355
00:32:43,474 --> 00:32:49,143
Guys, that's injun Joe.
Run!

356
00:32:49,145 --> 00:32:52,646
This here belong to any of you?

357
00:32:57,485 --> 00:33:00,085
Hah!

358
00:33:31,050 --> 00:33:34,351
