Yeah, Joe...
Partner.

376
00:35:55,605 --> 00:35:57,638
<i>Come on, move!
Let's move.</i>

377
00:35:57,640 --> 00:36:00,807
<i>Watch it. Watch it.
C'mon, hit me.</i>

