379
00:36:13,687 --> 00:36:16,187
<i>Come on, lefty.
All right, lefty.</i>

380
00:36:16,189 --> 00:36:19,924
<i>Get it out.
That's it, that's it.</i>

381
00:36:19,926 --> 00:36:22,459
Double hold.
Now, c'mon.

