00:38:24,298 --> 00:38:26,531
Ain't ya comin'?

394
00:38:26,533 --> 00:38:29,800
One map don't need
the two of us.

395
00:38:29,802 --> 00:38:33,537
I'll wait here.

396
00:39:00,963 --> 00:39:04,864
Go.

397
00:39:55,778 --> 00:39:59,979
Them goddamn wild boars.

398
00:39:59,981 --> 00:40:02,614
Hah!

399
00:40:17,897 --> 00:40:20,597
You had to sneeze.

400
00:40:23,835 --> 00:40:27,870
Muff's raft must've
washed away in the storm.

401
00:40:27,872 --> 00:40:32,441
I guess we'll have to take the
long way back to Hannibal.

402
00:40:32,443 --> 00:40:35,444
