gonna tar the head off of you...

403
00:40:35,446 --> 00:40:38,980
If she finds out you've been
out with me all this time.

404
00:40:39,716 --> 00:40:42,016
What?

405
00:40:42,985 --> 00:40:45,552
It's the old haunted house. So?

406
00:40:45,554 --> 00:40:49,689
