Ahh!

421
00:42:53,235 --> 00:42:55,968
<i>Quit your bellyachin' and dig.</i>

422
00:42:59,239 --> 00:43:04,075
<i>You sure about the fireplace?
Ain't that what I said?</i>

423
00:43:05,912 --> 00:43:08,712
