00:44:23,076 --> 00:44:26,844
Go ahead and knock it off.
Quick.

436
00:44:26,846 --> 00:44:30,247
<i>Good lord! Look at you.</i>

437
00:44:30,249 --> 00:44:33,817
<i>You beautiful money.</i>

438
00:44:33,819 --> 00:44:36,885
Hello, Texas and the good life.

439
00:44:38,355 --> 00:44:40,254
<i>No!</i>

440
00:44:40,256 --> 00:44:42,623
<i>What?</i>
We'll wait.

441
00:44:42,625 --> 00:44:45,325
<i>'Til after the trial.
I've got to testify.</i>

442
00:44:45,327 --> 00:44:48,828
Make sure muff takes the blame
for doc's murder.

443
00:44:48,830 --> 00:44:54,066
- Where're we gonna keep it in the meantime?
- Number two under the cross.

444
00:44:54,068 --> 00:44:58,303
<i>Load up. I've got some things to take care
of in town.</i> Number two under the cross.

445
00:45:00,040 --> 00:45:05,977
Look who's doin'
all the darn work.

446
00:45:05,979 --> 00:45:09,246
<i>Raining like pouring pigs
on a rawhide. Well...</i>

447
00:45:25,930 --> 00:45:28,030
no more map.

448
00:45:28,032 --> 00:45:30,766
No more muff.

449
00:45:37,707 --> 00:45:39,807
<i>Number two under the cross.</i>

450
00:45:39,809 --> 00:45:44,711
<i>If you ask me, we're better
off not knowin'. Why?</i>

451
00:45:44,713 --> 00:45:48,281
