fighter on the whole Mississippi.

454
00:45:56,424 --> 00:45:59,825
No.
My pap's the best.

455
00:45:59,827 --> 00:46:03,128
Taught injun Joe
everything he knows.

456
00:46:03,130 --> 00:46:06,297
Your pap knew injun Joe?

457
00:46:06,299 --> 00:46:08,832
